"title": "5115: Peter, preacher and teacher",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5115",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Peter preached mainly to the Jews. He taught both through his preaching and his letters.</p>\n<h2>Peter's commission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:17\">JHN 21:17</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Peter quoted from the OT in his teaching</h2>\n<p>Referring to the death of Judas:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:16\">ACT 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:20\">ACT 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:20\">ACT 2:16–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:25-Acts2:28\">ACT 2:25–2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:34-Acts2:35\">ACT 2:34–2:35</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:22-Acts3:23\">ACT 3:22–3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:24-1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:24–1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6-1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:6–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:5-1Pet3:6\">1PE 3:5–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:12\">1PE 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:14\">1PE 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:20\">1PE 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:18\">1PE 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:5-2Pet2:9\">2PE 2:5–2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Peter taught about Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>About the life and miracles of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22\">ACT 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36-Acts10:39\">ACT 10:36–10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17-2Pet1:18\">2PE 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h3>About Jesus Christ's suffering and death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:13-Acts3:15\">ACT 3:13–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10\">ACT 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30\">ACT 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:39\">ACT 10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:22–2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>About the resurrection of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24\">ACT 2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:31-Acts2:32\">ACT 2:31–2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:15\">ACT 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10\">ACT 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30\">ACT 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:40-Acts10:41\">ACT 10:40–10:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3\">1PE 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>About the ascension and exaltation of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:33\">ACT 2:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:36\">ACT 2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:13\">ACT 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>About the second coming of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:4\">1PE 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10-2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:10–3:13</a></p>\n<h2>Peter taught about salvation through repentance and faith in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:43\">ACT 10:43</a></p>\n<h2>Peter taught that God cared for all people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34\">ACT 10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7-Acts15:9\">ACT 15:7–15:9</a></p>\n<h2>Peter wrote his first letter to encourage Christians</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1\">1PE 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">1PE 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1\">1PE 2:1</a> <em>He exhorted them to live holy lives</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a> <em>They must obey authority</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:161\">1PE 3:161</a>PE <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:16\">4:12–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a> <em>God will vindicate and save his people.</em></p>\n<h2>Peter wrote his second letter to strengthen Christians who were at risk from false teaching</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:12\">2PE 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16\">2PE 1:16</a> <em>He reminded them of the truth of the gospel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:3</a> <em>He warned them of the judgment awaiting false teachers</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a> <em>They must keep alive their hope in the coming day of the Lord.</em></p>",
